{"tid":297017,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"男持刀闖欅坂46握手會　行刺對象是平手友梨奈","createTime":"2017-06-25T06:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T17:08:14.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c252fa194dc33f9bb186f89964f6eaf5696962b","tid":297017,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"據日媒報導，被捕無業男子阿部凌平現年24歲，昨晚他憑櫸坂46今年4月發行單曲《大協和音》內的握手券入場，並成功通過金屬探測器，並排在成員柿崎芽實與平手友梨奈的隊伍。由於事發時場面混亂，大會一度將活動暫停，在確認沒人受傷及把男子帶走後，握手會才繼續舉行。今天欅坂46在幕張國際展覽中心亦有活動，也如期舉行。平手友梨奈在欅坂隊中一枝獨秀，出道一年推出四支單曲都登上銷量榜冠軍，先前的暢銷單曲《大協和音》累積75萬張，成為2017上半年最暢銷單曲第4名，7月19日更將發行首張專輯《潔白物不想被沾污》。（娛樂中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170625/640_3575f399c96f3db20b8e4c1078f6d347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170625%2F640_3575f399c96f3db20b8e4c1078f6d347.jpg&h=87bbd2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8eddb38d75701c5040ed102cfc5da3767bfda9","tid":297017,"uid":1921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:30:09.000Z","msg":"大協和音"},{"pid":"2d491d0192345f6277eaeece48052b2c5f97258b","tid":297017,"uid":60170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大協和音</blockquote><br />\nD記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e90a19d7305416bf80ffbec1a2a4e85b5c99abb","tid":297017,"uid":67591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"大信和音"},{"pid":"e86c8bfd506951e80dd87ab46cd0dbb38b76ac63","tid":297017,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"あ"},{"pid":"f6506362305bde6d745eaf1db71188655128ae89","tid":297017,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15